title: Clay Travis and Buck Sexton Show H3 – Sep 2 2021

description:
Liz Wheeler, host of The Liz Wheeler Show podcast, breaks down the recall election of second worst governor in the country, California's Gavin Newsom. The left continues its assault to discredit Governor DeSantis. Requiring customers to be vaccinated can draw $5,000 fines starting soon in Florida. Taliban tries to rebrand itself as "New Taliban." Biden is cratering in the polls. China bans kids from playing online video games during the week.
